    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Test, verify, and weigh with confidence using the complete ToolTreaux Acid Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale. This all-in-one gold verification set combines professional acid-testing solutions with a high-precision digital scale, giving you everything you need to determine both karat purity and weight in one convenient kit. Complete Testing &amp; Weighing System</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux Testing Kit Acid Solution, Stone, Neutralizer and Scale (7 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Test, verify, and weigh with confidence using the complete ToolTreaux Acid Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale. This all-in-one gold verification set combines professional acid-testing solutions with a high-precision digital scale, giving you everything you need to determine both karat purity and weight in one convenient kit.</p>\n  <p>Complete Testing &amp; Weighing System</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>COMPLETE TESTING &amp; WEIGHING KIT - All-in-one set includes testing acid, neutralizing solution, testing stone, and a precision digital pocket scale for verifying both gold purity and weight with one convenient purchase.</li>\n    <li>ACCURATE ACID TESTING - Quickly determine karat authenticity by using the reliable scratch-and-test method; ideal for evaluating scrap gold, coins, and jewelry before buying, selling, or appraising.</li>\n    <li>HIGH PRECISION DIGITAL SCALE - Sensitive sensors deliver dependable measurements in grams, ounces, tola, carats, and grains, making it perfect for weighing precious metals and small valuables.</li>\n    <li>COMPACT PROFESSIONAL DESIGN - Portable scale features a clear backlit LCD display, tare function, counting capability, and auto shut-off, while durable squeeze bottles allow controlled, mess-free acid application.</li>\n    <li>IDEAL FOR BUYERS, SELLERS &amp; COLLECTORS - Great for pawn shops, jewelry resellers, estate evaluations, and hobbyists who need a reliable way to test gold authenticity and confirm weight with confidence.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73464/eawly5kq5xlIPCZtZLPASgIsTiXPHW-metadGVzdGluZ19raXRfc2NhbGVfdmFyLmpwZw==-.jpg\" alt=\"Test, verify, and weigh with confidence using the complete ToolTreaux Acid Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> TTX-ATK-SILQ-BUN</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This comprehensive kit includes: (1) 0.5oz Bottle Testing Acid (1) 0.5oz Bottle Neutralizing Solution (1) Gold Testing Stone (1) Portable Digital Pocket Scale with LCD Display</p>\n  <p>The testing acid is potent and effective, allowing for dozens of tests. Each solution comes housed in durable, shatter-resistant squeeze bottles for precise drop control and safer handling.</p>\n  <p>The included digital pocket scale features high-precision sensors capable of measuring in five units: grams (g), ounces (oz), tola (tl), carats (ct), and grains (gn) - making it ideal for weighing gold jewelry, scrap gold, bullion, coins, and other precious metals before or after testing.</p>\n  <p>GOLD TESTING METHOD</p>\n  <p>This acid testing method is best used on raw or scrap gold due to the strength of the solution. When testing finished jewelry or delicate pieces, always scratch the item in an inconspicuous area to avoid visible damage.</p>\n  <p>Instructions:</p>\n  <p>-Scratch the gold item onto the testing stone, leaving a visible streak. -Apply a small drop of 10K testing solution onto the streak. -If the gold is 10K or higher, the streak will remain unchanged. -If the gold is lower than 10K, the streak will dissolve or fade. -Apply an equal amount of neutralizing solution after each test. -Thoroughly rinse and neutralize the testing stone before additional testing.</p>\n  <p>High-Precision Digital Pocket Scale Features</p>\n  <p>The included compact scale adds professional-level accuracy to your gold evaluation process: -High-precision sensors for accurate measurement -Backlit LCD display for clear readings -Tare (zero-out) function for container weighing -Counting function for small items -One-minute automatic shut-off -Compact, portable design for bench-top or store use</p>\n  <p>Maximum Capacities by Unit: Grams: 500g Ounces: 17oz Tola: 40tl Carats: 2500ct Grains: 7716gn</p>\n  <p>Whether you are verifying scrap gold purchases, testing estate jewelry, or confirming bullion weight, this digital scale ensures precise measurements to complement your karat testing results.</p>\n  <p>Ideal For: -Jewelry buyers &amp; resellers -Pawn shops -Coin and bullion collectors -Estate sale professionals -Precious metal hobbyists -Repair benches and appraisal work</p>\n  <p>IMPORTANT SAFETY NOTICE</p>\n  <p>Testing acids are corrosive and may cause burns. Always wear proper protective gloves and eye protection when handling. Avoid skin contact. Neutralize the testing acid after every use. Carefully read and follow all label instructions before use.</p>\n  <p>With both purity testing and precision weighing in one convenient kit, the ToolTreaux Gold Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale delivers accuracy, control, and professional-grade results every time.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
